bing|-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
bing: bing (Bandwidth ping)
bing:
bing: Bing is a point-to-point bandwidth measurement tool (hence the 'b'),
bing: based on ping.
bing: Bing determines the real (raw, as opposed to available or average)
bing: throughput on a link by measuring ICMP echo requests' round trip
bing: times for different packet sizes at each end of the link. 
bing:
bing: http://fgouget.free.fr/bing/index-en.shtml
bing:
bing: Packager: _PACKAGER on _BUILD_DATE
